Welcome!
Thank you for your interest in contributing to our Simple Interest Calculator project! Here's how you can help:

How to Contribute
You can contribute by:

-Adding new features.
-Fixing bugs.
-Improving documentation.
-Providing feedback.
-Getting Started
-Fork and clone the repository.
-Make your changes locally.
-Submit a pull request.

 Guidelines
-Follow coding conventions.
-Write clear commit messages.
-Test your changes.
-Update documentation if needed.

Code of Conduct
-Be respectful and considerate towards others.

License
-By contributing, you agree to the Apache License 2.0.

Contact
-If you have any questions, reach out to us at [contact@email.com].

Thank You!
Your contributions make a difference!

